d metric of 95.57% at\nthe Traffic Analysis Zone level and 92.39% at the stop level, compared to the\nground-truth estimates inferred from the state-of-practice trip-chaining\nmethods.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Nov 2019 19:38:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-15"}
