ity and relatively high intrinsic X-ray luminosity, it is undetected by\nthe 105 month Swift-BAT survey, underscoring the importance of multi-wavelength\nselection for obtaining the most complete census of the most hidden black\nholes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Nov 2019 21:01:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-08"}
