 average variational method in the calculus\nof variations that we have employed is in contrast to an average method in PDE\nthat we applied in \\cite {CW} to obtain sharp growth estimates for warping\nfunctions in multiply warped product manifolds.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Nov 2019 22:59:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-15"}
