oposed model demonstrates improved performance at capturing\nthe distribution of extreme precipitation over Community Atmosphere Model (CAM)\n5.2 forecasts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Nov 2019 01:03:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-03"}
