hly uncertain. The behavior of comet\nBorisov during its inbound leg is observationally consistent with dynamically\nnew comets observed in our solar system, suggesting some similarities between\nthe two.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Nov 2019 02:34:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 23 Dec 2019 21:03:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-05"}
