d power consumption is\nconsidered, for which the MM-based alternating optimization still works.\nNumerical results demonstrate the similar or superior performance of all the\nabove proposed schemes over the existing benchmarks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Nov 2019 02:43:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-21"}
