ion of coronal mass ejections take place, thus significantly improving\nour understanding of the region connecting the Sun to the heliosphere.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Nov 2019 13:14:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-20"}
